Package: biobakeryUtils
Type: Package
Title: Manipulate and Analyze Data from the BioBakery Suite
Version: 0.8.0
Authors@R: person("Giacomo", "Antonello",
                  email = "giacomoantonello1@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for importing, formatting, and
    manipulating data from the BioBakery suite, including tools for
    preparing data for use with 'phyloseq' and 'TreeSummarizedExperiment'
    objects.
